      "message": "Now I\u0027m wondering about getLocation(Expression) and whether Expressions need long term storage Location for their values at all.  Aren\u0027t we going to just use them in a way that a simple signature like this would work?\n\n   std::array\u003cskvm::Val,16\u003e vals(const Expression\u0026);\n\nOr do we support non-Variable lvalue expressions like `(foo ? x : y) \u003d 5.0;` ?",
